/*

"src": list of mono src files. Position in array corressponds to position in cascade.
"dest": specify CSS file mono src compiles to.

*/

{
  "src": [
    "app",
    "nav"
  ],
  "dest": "out/main.css"
}

/*

In future src files could be bundled into seperate packages.

Declarations within packages could be namespaced to avoid
conflicting styles.

Something like:

{
  "src": {
    "foo": "../foo.css",
    "bar": "../bar.css"
  },
}

Styles could then be namespaced with package name, i.e:

foo.css:

.foo h1 {}
.foo body .main {}
.foo div.heading {}

bar.css:

.bar p {}
.bar div.heading {}

*/